## 🎉 Great News!

Your SSH is **already working** to all three Raspberry Pis! You successfully connected to:
- ✅ blackroad-pi (192.168.4.64)
- ✅ lucidia (192.168.4.38)
- ✅ alice (192.168.4.49)

